Content Management

ConservationSpace allows you to work with different types of system objects and to manipulate their content.

Widgets:

  • Widgets are tools used for interacting in CS, such as reading or editing data in the system.
  • Widgets are used to configure the Landing Pages of the Objects.
  • Look at Widgets as the visual building blocks used to hold all the data about an object.

 

Each time the object is saved, a new version is created
